ading\" id=\"h-hong-kong-s-leader-can-create-new-laws-on-their-own\"><strong>7. \u9999\u6e2f\u9886\u5bfc\u4eba\u53ef\u4ee5\u81ea\u884c\u5236\u5b9a\u65b0\u7684\u6cd5\u5f8b<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>\u6839\u636e\u65b0\u6cd5\uff0c\u9999\u6e2f\u884c\u653f\u957f\u5b98\u53ef\u968f\u65f6\u4ee5\u201c\u7ef4\u62a4\u56fd\u5bb6\u5b89\u5168\u201d\u7684\u540d\u4e49\uff0c\u81ea\u884c\u5236\u5b9a\u9644\u5c5e\u6cd5\u4f8b\u3002  \u9644\u5c5e\u6cd5\u4f8b\u53ef\u7acb\u5373\u751f\u6548\uff0c\u8fdd\u53cd\u8005\u6700\u9ad8\u53ef\u88ab\u5224\u5904\u4e03\u5e74\u76d1\u7981\u3002    <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u4ece\u7406\u8bba\u4e0a\u6765\u8bf4\uff0c\u9644\u5c5e\u6cd5\u4f8b\u4e0d\u5e94\u8d85\u51fa23\u6761\u7684\u9002\u7528\u8303\u56f4\uff0c\u4f4623\u6761\u6a21\u7cca\u548c\u5bbd\u6cdb\u7684\u63aa\u8f9e\uff0c\u63d0\u4f9b\u7ed9\u5f53\u5c40\u5e7f\u9614\u7684\u81ea\u7531\u88c1\u91cf\u7a7a\u95f4\u3002<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"aimc-ignore wp-block-image size-large\"><div style=\"position:relative\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"433\" src=\"https:\/\/zh.amnesty.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/271057-2048x865-1-1024x433.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"aiic-ignore wp-image-11928\" srcset=\"https:\/\/zh.amnesty.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/271057-2048x865-1-1024x433.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/zh.amnesty.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/271057-2048x865-1-300x127.jpg 300w, https:\/\/zh.amnesty.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/271057-2048x865-1-768x324.jpg 768w, https:\/\/zh.amnesty.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/271057-2048x865-1-1536x649.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/zh.amnesty.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/271057-2048x865-1-1421x600.jpg 1421w, https:\/\/zh.amnesty.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/271057-2048x865-1-734x310.jpg 734w, https:\/\/zh.amnesty.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/271057-2048x865-1-170x72.jpg 170w, https:\/\/zh.amnesty.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/271057-2048x865-1-341x144.jpg 341w, https:\/\/zh.amnesty.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\